Test cases for even-numbered Requirements
	Test Case #
	<precondition>
	<action>
	<postcondition>

2a) solution must initiate a ship launch when system detects no active ships
	Test Case 1
	game is running and no ships are on screen
	no action
	game has launched a ship

2c) solution must display the appropriate image based on the type of ship that is active
	Test Case 1
	game is open and running, configuration set to only one type of ship
	watch images of ships
	image of ship matches the type of ship configured
	-repeat for each ship type
	
4) solution must end the game when the user clicks the left mouse button
	Test Case 1
	game is open and running
	click left mouse button
	game closes
   
	Test Case 2
	game is open and running
	press any key other than left mouse click, right mouse click, esc, or space
	game remains open and nothing happens

6) solution must end the game if the user has not initiated a missile launch in the last 5 minutes
	Test Case 1
	game is open and running
 	leave game idle for 5 minutes
	game closes

	Test Case 2
	game is open and running
	leave game idle between 1 and <5 minutes
	game remains open

	Test Case 3
	game is open and running
	press some keys other than esc, left mouse click, right mouse click, or space for 5 minutes
	game closes

	Test Case 4
	game is open and running, has been idle for 4 minutes
	press space or right click once, then wait 1 minute
	game launches missile and remains open
	
   
